                                            <span class="text-xs sm:text-base text-gray-400">
                                                Why is this system necessary?
                                            </span>
                                        </li>
                                        <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs sm:text-base md:text-xl lg:text-base xl:text-xl">
                                            Since it is not possible to install sensors to measure the indoor environment 
                                            in the center of a room or other living space, sensors are often installed on walls. 
                                            Therefore, the discrepancy between the values at the wall and those in the living space is an issue.
                                            <br>
                                            This system uses machine learning to predict and correct sensor values in a
                                            living space, and visualizes the results in real time.
                                        </span>
